headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Northern Trust (NTRS) After Its Strong Five Year Run?
summary: If you are wondering whether Northern Trust stock still offers value after its recent run, or if the price already reflects the good news, this article walks through the key points to help you weigh that up. At a last close of US$148.63, Northern Trust has recent returns of 2.1% over 7 days, 5.6% over 30 days, 6.7% year to date, 37.7% over 1 year, 68.7% over 3 years, and 94.0% over 5 years.
